1. Download the .java file from the github here

2. Change the first line once downloaded to be in whatever package you wish for it to be in

3. Start the program, and Sophia will tell you what to do from there.


(In case you it is somehow not clear)

4. Input your name into the text box and press the button to submit

5. Set your initial mood so Sophia knows how your feeling

6. Type your problem and Sophia will try her best to help.
